"title": "8358: weakness, physical",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8358",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Lack of human strength may have a number of causes. Believers should be caring and compassionate towards the weak.</p>\n<h2>Causes of human physical weakness</h2>\n<h3>Sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3\">ROM 8:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:10\">PSA 90:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6\">ROM 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:2\">HEB 5:2</a></p>\n<h3>Divine action</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:25\">GEN 32:25</a></strong> <em>Through wrestling with God, Jacob carried a physical reminder for the rest of his life.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:32\">GEN 32:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:21\">HEB 11:21</a></p>\n<h3>Disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:20\">JDG 16:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:7\">JDG 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:11\">JDG 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:13\">JDG 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:17\">JDG 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:7\">JOB 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:17\">EZK 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:7\">EZK 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:30\">1CO 11:30</a></p>\n<h3>Satanic action</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:12\">ISA 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17-Mark9:18\">MRK 9:17–9:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:11\">LUK 13:11</a></p>\n<h3>Disease or disability</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:2\">PSA 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:10\">PSA 31:9–31:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:7\">JHN 5:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:13-Gal4:14\">GAL 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Weakness from birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:2\">ACT 3:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Weakness in old age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:1\">GEN 27:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:34-2Sam19:37\">2SA 19:34–19:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:1\">1KI 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Persecution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:30\">2CO 11:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:14-Num11:15\">NUM 11:14–11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:6\">1KI 19:3–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:32\">MAT 27:32</a> <em>The physical weakness of Jesus Christ after flogging led to Simon carrying the cross</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19-Acts14:20\">ACT 14:19–14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:3\">1CO 2:3</a> <em>Weakness and fear are often associated</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:23–11:29</a></p>\n<h3>Being faced with opposition</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:18\">NUM 13:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:29\">2SA 3:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>Corporate weakness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:12\">2CH 20:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:36\">LEV 26:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:15\">JDG 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:1\">2SA 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:6\">LAM 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Believers' responsibility to the weak</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:35\">ACT 20:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:1\">PSA 41:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:4\">EZK 34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1\">ROM 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9\">1CO 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:22\">1CO 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">1TH 5:14</a></p>\n<h2>The weakness of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></p>",
